# Instructions on how to install verobs and WebgraF
# For usage read on in the readme files
#
# Ulf Andrae, SMHI, 2006

# Install WebgraF

 - Set your WebgraF main directory in WebgraF/bin/WebgraF.pl where :

 # Change you working directory here        
 #############################################
 $WEBGRAF_BASE = "$SOME_PATH/WebgraF" ;
 #############################################

 - Add $SOME_PATH/WebgraF/bin/WebgraF to you path

 Open $SOME_PATH/WebgraF/index.html in you browser

 Read on in the README_WebgraF for further usage


# Install verobs

External libraries needed : magics, emoslib, eclib

At ecgate
Edit the monitor/src/Makefile and define where you have your source/lib/bin

   BINDIR=$(SCRATCH)/bin
   MODDIR=$(SCRATCH)/lib
   LIBDIR=$(SCRATCH)/lib
   SRCDIR=$(SCRATCH)/monitor/src

For other machines a new entry in the Makefile has to be introduced

Copmile by ; cd $SRCDIR ; gmake


Read on in the README_verobs for further usage


